<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 16:07:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>民意调查发现，75％的犹太以色列人拒绝美国将加沙战争转移到新阶段的要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/75-of-jewish-israelis-reject-u-s-demand-to-shift-gaza-war-to-new-phase-poll-finds/0000018c-caa4-d4e1-ad8f-feb5bdda0000</link><description>56%的阿拉伯受访者表示以色列应该屈服于美国的压力，大多数左翼犹太人也同意战争应该转向精确瞄准哈马斯领导人</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 15:19:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/75-of-jewish-israelis-reject-u-s-demand-to-shift-gaza-war-to-new-phase-poll-finds/0000018c-caa4-d4e1-ad8f-feb5bdda0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼议员威胁：“我们将与哈马斯、真主党打交道，然后是最高法院”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/far-right-lawmaker-threatens-we-will-deal-with-hamas-hezbollah-then-the-supreme-court/0000018c-caa6-d4e1-ad8f-feb71d610000</link><description>高等法院周一否决了一项重要的司法政变法后，来自 Ben-Gvir 领导的 Otzma Yehudit 党的 MK Tzvika Foghel 在 X 上发布了这一威胁。战时内阁成员甘茨称这种比较“卑鄙可耻”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 15:16:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/far-right-lawmaker-threatens-we-will-deal-with-hamas-hezbollah-then-the-supreme-court/0000018c-caa6-d4e1-ad8f-feb71d610000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军慈善机构提拔支持“扁平化”加沙的分析师，称自由主义者是“犹太国家的敌人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-charity-promotes-analyst-who-supports-flattening-gaza-loathes-liberal-values/0000018c-ca11-ddba-abad-cab17ea40000</link><description>以色列国防军之友邀请颇具争议的评论员埃利亚胡·约西安 (Eliyahu Yossian) 在一群受益者面前发表讲话。他此前曾声称，以色列应该在对 10 月 7 日大屠杀的立即反应中杀害 50,000 名加沙人</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:53:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-charity-promotes-analyst-who-supports-flattening-gaza-loathes-liberal-values/0000018c-ca11-ddba-abad-cab17ea40000</guid></item><item><title>3000万年前埃及的早期猴子吃什么？现在我们知道了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-02/ty-article/what-did-early-monkeys-eat-in-egypt-30-million-years-ago-now-we-know/0000018c-ca62-ddba-abad-cae32e5c0000</link><description>根据对 3400 万至 2900 万年前猴子化石牙齿的分析，缺乏广泛的牙釉质碎裂表明它们都吃软食。换句话说，水果</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:08:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-02/ty-article/what-did-early-monkeys-eat-in-egypt-30-million-years-ago-now-we-know/0000018c-ca62-ddba-abad-cae32e5c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列必须立即撤出加沙。现在是人质，后来是辛瓦尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-get-out-of-gaza-immediately-hostages-now-sinwar-later/0000018c-ca03-d4e1-ad8f-feb384af0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:06:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-get-out-of-gaza-immediately-hostages-now-sinwar-later/0000018c-ca03-d4e1-ad8f-feb384af0000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其拘留了 33 名涉嫌为以色列从事间谍活动的人，并正在寻找另外 13 名据信与摩萨德有联系的人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/turkey-detains-33-people-suspected-of-spying-for-israel/0000018c-ca73-d4e1-ad8f-fef3c4380000</link><description>嫌疑人因涉嫌计划代表以色列情报机构开展包括“追捕、袭击和绑架”居住在土耳其的外国人在内的活动而被拘留。辛贝特领导人表示，他们将在“每个地方”追捕哈马斯领导人，包括土耳其</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 13:53:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/turkey-detains-33-people-suspected-of-spying-for-israel/0000018c-ca73-d4e1-ad8f-fef3c4380000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院法官以决定性多数宣布内塔尼亚胡的司法政变宣告结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/decisive-majority-of-israels-high-court-justices-declares-netanyahus-judicial-coup-dead/0000018c-c9c4-ddba-abad-cbe59ebf0000</link><description>反对微弱选票的警告最终证明是虚假的操纵，因为这会在战争时期分裂人民。内塔尼亚胡对下一个决定更感兴趣：禁止司法部长宣布他不适合担任公职的法律</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 12:30:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/decisive-majority-of-israels-high-court-justices-declares-netanyahus-judicial-coup-dead/0000018c-c9c4-ddba-abad-cbe59ebf0000</guid></item><item><title>新星狂欢节幸存者起诉以色列安全机构，要求赔偿 2 亿谢克尔，理由是其未能阻止哈马斯的屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/nova-survivors-sue-israeli-security-agencies-for-200m-over-hamas-massacre/0000018c-c969-d4e1-ad8f-fdf974c20000</link><description>“即使人们担心恐怖分子渗透到该地区，他们也没有驱散狂欢……这令人难以理解” ■ 哈马斯大屠杀幸存者提起的史无前例的诉讼认为，以色列国防军、辛贝特和以色列警察疏忽大意</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 12:22:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/nova-survivors-sue-israeli-security-agencies-for-200m-over-hamas-massacre/0000018c-c969-d4e1-ad8f-fdf974c20000</guid></item><item><title>警告赎罪日战争迫在眉睫的摩萨德前负责人去世，享年 98 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/former-mossad-head-who-warned-of-imminent-yom-kippur-war-dies-at-98/0000018c-c98b-ddba-abad-cbab791f0000</link><description>兹维·扎米尔警告说，如果“以色列政策没有发生深远的变化，战争就在预料之中” ■ 这位前摩萨德主席留下了卓越的服务遗产，摩萨德和以色列总统热烈纪念</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 11:39:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/former-mossad-head-who-warned-of-imminent-yom-kippur-war-dies-at-98/0000018c-c98b-ddba-abad-cbab791f0000</guid></item><item><title>丹尼斯·罗斯：在加沙，“内塔尼亚胡的极右翼部长并没有生活在现实中”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-02/ty-article-podcast/dennis-ross-on-gaza-netanyahus-far-right-ministers-arent-living-in-reality/0000018c-c6bc-ddba-abad-c6bd77b30000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 11:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-02/ty-article-podcast/dennis-ross-on-gaza-netanyahus-far-right-ministers-arent-living-in-reality/0000018c-c6bc-ddba-abad-c6bd77b30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长称本-格维尔“越界”并干扰警方批准抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-says-ben-gvir-crossed-the-line-to-interfere-with-police-approvals-of-protests/0000018c-c94a-d4e1-ad8f-fdfbb6a20000</link><description>总检察长警告说，以色列国家安全部长告诉警方禁止左翼哈达什党举行抗议活动，这已经越界了。本-格维尔的办公室表示，总检察长“有一个非常明确的议程”，并且讨厌他</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 10:26:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-says-ben-gvir-crossed-the-line-to-interfere-with-police-approvals-of-protests/0000018c-c94a-d4e1-ad8f-fdfbb6a20000</guid></item><item><title>画面中缺失：哈马斯袭击前后的以色列家庭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/missing-from-the-frame-israeli-families-before-and-after-hamas-attack/0000018c-c579-d6c4-ab8d-e5fd1f6a0000</link><description>有你和没有你：一个特别的摄影项目展示了 10 月 7 日家庭成员被哈马斯抓走之前和之后拍摄的照片</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 10:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/missing-from-the-frame-israeli-families-before-and-after-hamas-attack/0000018c-c579-d6c4-ab8d-e5fd1f6a0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦和阿拉伯囚犯报告称，自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列监狱看守的暴力行为激增</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-arab-prisoners-report-surge-in-violence-by-israeli-guards-since-oct-7/0000018c-c6a2-ddba-abad-c6a3a6920000</link><description>以色列北部一所监狱的安全拘留者报告称，他们遭到狱警的殴打，并威胁称，如果他们拒绝亲吻以色列国旗，就会遭受暴力袭击。 ■ 司法部警告监狱部门，必须依法对待囚犯</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 07:41:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-arab-prisoners-report-surge-in-violence-by-israeli-guards-since-oct-7/0000018c-c6a2-ddba-abad-c6a3a6920000</guid></item><item><title>美国在该地区海军存在的减少对以色列来说不是好兆头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/reduced-u-s-naval-presence-in-the-region-does-not-bode-well-for-israel/0000018c-c6e1-ddba-abad-c6e189a60000</link><description>真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉可能将美国的重新部署解读为承担更多风险的机会 ■ 本杰明·内塔尼亚胡和美国总统乔·拜登最近进行了一系列紧张的对话，主要集中在以色列领导人对巴勒斯坦权力机构的不屑一顾的态度</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 04:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/reduced-u-s-naval-presence-in-the-region-does-not-bode-well-for-israel/0000018c-c6e1-ddba-abad-c6e189a60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院判定内塔尼亚胡及其盗贼团伙惨败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-deals-netanyahu-and-his-band-of-thieves-a-decisive-defeat/0000018c-c74d-ddba-abad-c7ede2eb0000</link><description>周日最高法院以一票之差恢复了对以色列国的形容词“民主”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 04:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-deals-netanyahu-and-his-band-of-thieves-a-decisive-defeat/0000018c-c74d-ddba-abad-c7ede2eb0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯称加沙人质只能“按照他们的条件”释放；以色列空袭黎巴嫩、叙利亚目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article-live/idf-soldier-killed-in-gaza-far-right-ministers-call-for-control-of-gaza-settlements/0000018c-c81b-ddba-abad-cabbb6f60000</link><description>以色列空军袭击叙利亚，摧毁黎巴嫩南部真主党目标 ■ 以色列国防军在加沙近东救济工程处一所学校附近找到哈马斯火箭发射器 ■ 报告：33 人因涉嫌与摩萨德合作而在土耳其被捕 ■ 阵亡以色列国防军士兵的父母向布林肯表示：“阻止战争将是历史性的错误。 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵丧生；至少 133 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙 21,978 人死亡，57,697 人受伤</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 03:04:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article-live/idf-soldier-killed-in-gaza-far-right-ministers-call-for-control-of-gaza-settlements/0000018c-c81b-ddba-abad-cabbb6f60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院驳斥内塔尼亚胡的独裁谎言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-01/ty-article/.highlight/israels-supreme-court-strikes-down-netanyahus-autocratic-lies/0000018c-c643-d6c4-ab8d-e7f74d2a0000</link><description>这是以色列历史上最重要的案件之一：法院的裁决推翻了内塔尼亚胡政府对以色列社会极不受欢迎的神权吞并主义接管，以及随之而来的令人震惊的荒谬谎言</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 20:54:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-01/ty-article/.highlight/israels-supreme-court-strikes-down-netanyahus-autocratic-lies/0000018c-c643-d6c4-ab8d-e7f74d2a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列央行四年来首次降息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/bank-of-israel-cuts-interest-rate-for-first-time-in-two-years/0000018c-c6bc-d6c4-ab8d-e7bc10390000</link><description>由于通胀缓和以及加沙战争对经济前景的担忧，失业率下降了四分之一个百分点至 4.5%。央行现在担心的是政府支出急剧增加，因为它修改了2024年预算以满足战争需要</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 20:54:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/bank-of-israel-cuts-interest-rate-for-first-time-in-two-years/0000018c-c6bc-d6c4-ab8d-e7bc10390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大学停课八名声称在社交媒体帖子上支持哈马斯的学生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-university-suspends-eight-students-claiming-they-supported-hamas-on-social-media/0000018c-c69a-ddba-abad-c6bb88f60000</link><description>海法大学采取这一行动之前，校长声称学生的继续存在可能会引发“极端情况”。自 10 月 7 日以来，超过 100 名以色列学生（几乎全是阿拉伯人）因涉嫌表达支持哈马斯而面临纪律处分</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 20:39:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-university-suspends-eight-students-claiming-they-supported-hamas-on-social-media/0000018c-c69a-ddba-abad-c6bb88f60000</guid></item><item><title>这位拯救以色列脆弱民主的女人——暂时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/the-woman-who-saved-israels-fragile-democracy-for-now/0000018c-c69a-d6c4-ab8d-e7beabb30000</link><description>前最高法院院长埃丝特·哈尤特周一主持了一项裁决，有效地终止了政府的司法改革，为以色列社会带来了巨大的帮助。但以色列仍然像以前一样分裂，并且在战争结束后仍然如此</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 20:22:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/the-woman-who-saved-israels-fragile-democracy-for-now/0000018c-c69a-d6c4-ab8d-e7beabb30000</guid></item></channel></rss>